ania/11/mainevent|title=Wrestlemania XI main event|publisher=WWE|accessdate=2014-01-23}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sort|12|[[WrestleMania XII]]}}\n| {{dts|1996-03-31}}\n| [[Anaheim, California|Anaheim]], [[California]]\n| [[Honda Center|Arrowhead Pond of Anaheim]]\n| 18,853\n| [[Bret Hart]] (c) vs. [[Shawn Michaels]] in a 60-Minute [[Iron Man match]] for the [[WWF World Heavyweight Championship]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/shows/wrestlemania/12/mainevent|title=Wrestlemania XII main event|publisher=WWE|accessdate=2014-01-23}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sort|13|[[WrestleMania 13]]}}\n| {{dts|1997-03-23}}\n| [[Rosemont, Illinois|Rosemont]], [[Illinois]]\n| [[Allstate Arena|Rosemont Horizon]]\n| 18,197\n| [[Sid Eudy|Sycho Sid]] (c) vs. [[The Undertaker]] in a [[No Disqualification match]] for the [[WWF World Heavyweight Championship]] \n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/shows/wrestlemania/13/mainevent|title=Wrestlemania 13 main event|publisher=WWE|accessdate=2014-01-23}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sort|14|[[WrestleMania XIV]]}}\n| {{dts|1998-03-29}}\n| [[Boston]], [[Massachusetts]]\n| [[TD Garden|FleetCenter]]\n| 19,028\n| [[Shawn Michaels]] (c) vs. [[Stone Cold Steve Austin]] for the [[WWF World Heavyweight Championship]] with [[special guest enforcer]] [[Mike Tyson]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/shows/wrestlemania/14/results|title=Wrestlemania XIV results|publisher=WWE|accessdate=2014-01-23}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sort|15|[[WrestleMania XV]]}}\n| {{dts|1999-03-28}}\n| [[Philadelphia]], [[Pennsylvania]]\n| [[Wells Fargo Center (Philadelphia)|First Union Center]]\n| 19,514\n| [[Dwayne Johnson|The Rock]] (c) vs. [[Stone Cold Steve Austin]] in a [[No Disqualification match]] for the [[WWF Championship]] with [[special guest referee]] [[Mick Foley|Mankind]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/shows/wrestlemania/15/results|title=Wrestlemania XV results|publisher=WWE|accessdate=2014-01-23}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sort|16|[[WrestleMania 2000]]}}\n| {{dts|2000-04-02}}\n| [[Anaheim, Califor